comments: Vucevic (CHI) and Crowder (PHX) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Crowder (PHX) is already in White's (CHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Bradley (CHI) is already in Bridges' (PHX) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Bridges (PHX) reaches in and makes contact with Bradley's (CHI) arm as he is starting his upward shooting motion.
Hill (CHI) and Booker (PHX) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Crowder (PHX) is already in Hill's (CHI) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Crowder (PHX) makes contact with McKinnie's (CHI) arm during his drive during the penalty.
Bradley (CHI) legally contests Jackson's (PHX) driving shot attempt.
Jackson (PHX) and Hill (CHI) come together at the same spot and incidental contact occurs during rebounding.
Payton (PHX) briefly grasps Hill's (CHI) arm and marginal contact occurs as Payton is passing the ball.
Thomas (CHI) applies a stayed hand to Biyombo's (PHX) hip and immediately removes his hand as Biyombo begins his upward shooting motion.
Payton (PHX) legally contests Hill's (CHI) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hill (CHI) brings his hand forward towards Payton's (PHX) front and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Wainwright (PHX) and McKinnie (CHI) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Smith (PHX) is moving alongside Hill's (CHI) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
